---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="External Penetration Testing | Sheepdog Cyber Defense" description="External penetration testing for Texas businesses. Test your internet-facing systems from an attacker's perspective.">
  <section>
    <h1>External Penetration Testing</h1>
    <p class="lead">We test your internet-facing systems the way an attacker would see them—from the outside.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>What It Covers</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Websites and web applications</li>
      <li>Email servers and mail gateways</li>
      <li>VPNs and remote access solutions</li>
      <li>DNS infrastructure</li>
      <li>Cloud services (AWS, Azure, Google Cloud)</li>
      <li>Open ports and services</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <p>We start with reconnaissance—gathering information just like a real attacker would. Then we probe for vulnerabilities, misconfigurations, and weak points. Every finding is verified manually; we don't just run automated scans and call it done.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Deliverables</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Detailed findings report with screenshots and proof of concept</li>
      <li>Risk-rated vulnerabilities (Critical, High, Medium, Low)</li>
      <li>Remediation recommendations for each finding</li>
      <li>Executive summary for leadership</li>
      <li>Live debrief call to walk through results</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Typical Timeline</h2>
    <p>Most external tests complete within 1-2 weeks, depending on scope. We'll give you a timeline estimate before we start.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>What You'll Need</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Scope definition (what systems are in-scope)</li>
      <li>Access credentials (if applicable)</li>
      <li>Any existing documentation</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <a href="/contact" class="btn">Request a Quote</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  li {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
</style>
